caption.p: Effects of different concentrations of MWCNTSs and MeJA treatments on catalase (A, B), guaiacol peroxidase (C, D) and ascorbate peroxidase (E, F) activities in Satureja khuzistanica nodal segments cultures. Different letters indicate significant differences (Duncan’s multiple range test, p < 0.05). Bars represent means ± SD.
